@mistercrunch I made the change to move the hook to contrib locally, but it makes the ad hoq connection disappear. The models.py/Connection.get_hook currently points to:

```
elif self.conn_type == 'bigquery':
  return hooks.BigQueryHook(bigquery_conn_id=self.conn_id)
```

I could obviously update this to point to the contrib hooks directory instead, but this feels wrong. I see there's some plugin_manager stuff in the init py file. What do you recommend?
